<% layout("/layout/boilerplate") -%>

    <body>
        <div class="unique-privacy-header">
            <header class="page-header">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            </header>
            <main class="privacy-content">
                <section class="section">
                    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
                    <p>
                        Welcome to NestNova! Your privacy is of utmost importance to us. This Privacy Policy explains
                        how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our services.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="section">
                    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email, phone number, and payment details.</li>
                        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Interaction with our website, including searches, bookings, and
                            preferences.</li>
                        <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> Approximate or precise location information to enhance user
                            experience.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                <section class="section">
                    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <p>Your information is used to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Process bookings and provide customer support.</li>
                        <li>Enhance security and detect fraud.</li>
                        <li>Send updates and promotional materials (only with your consent).</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                <section class="section">
                    <h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
                    <p>
                        We share your information only as needed with trusted third parties, such as payment processors,
                        service providers, and legal authorities (when required by law).
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="section">
                    <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
                    <p>
                        We retain your information for as long as it is necessary to provide our services, comply with
                        legal obligations, or resolve disputes.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="section">
                    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>You have the right to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Access and update your personal data.</li>
                        <li>Request deletion of your data, subject to legal obligations.</li>
                        <li>Opt out of marketing communications.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
                <section class="section">
                    <h2>7. Security Measures</h2>
                    <p>
                        We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data. However, no system is
                        entirely secure, and we encourage caution while sharing sensitive information online.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="section">
                    <h2>8. Updates to This Policy</h2>
                    <p>
                        We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We encourage you to review this page regularly
                        to stay informed of any changes.
                    </p>
                </section>
                <section class="section">
                    <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>
                        If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a
                            href="mailto:privacy@nestnova.com">privacy@nestnova.com</a>.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </main>
        </div>
    </body>